NAME triage

INPUT task
  Incident report or alert to triage

GOAL triage -> assessment
  Perform initial incident triage:
  - Severity classification: P0 (outage), P1 (degraded), P2 (minor), P3 (cosmetic)
  - Affected systems and blast radius
  - User impact estimate
  - Initial hypothesis (top 3 probable causes)
  - Recommended immediate actions (first 5 minutes)
  
  Be decisive. Triage is about speed, not certainty.
